    • model.Photo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Photo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Photo A photo object that contains the serialized photo object and some information about the photo (date/time uploaded, caption, tagList).
